const HomeStart = () => { return (

Getting Started With RING

Three easy steps to earn lifetime rewards
1
Buy RING

RING is available on the Binance Smart Chain Network.You can swap BNB for RING on PancakeSwap. Click on the button below to buy RING tokens.

BUY RING
2
Create a node

A RING-Node costs only 10 RING and has no on-going maintenance fees, subscriptions, or software to run.

CREATE A NODE
3
enjoy rewards

That’s it! You can create up to 100 nodes per wallet, rewards pay out every 4 hours, and there’s nothing else for you to do!

WATCH NETFLIX
) } export default HomeStart;
